        "content": "<p> See the Qur’ān: 7:65-74; 9:70; 11:50-60; 14:8-9; 22:42; 23:31-41; 25:38; 26:123-140; 38:12-13 ; 40:31; 41:13-16; 46:21-25; 50:12-13; 51:41-42; 53:50-55; 54:18-22; 69:6-8; 89:6-9. </p>",
